This paper deals with the problem of maximizing the sampling time of RF harvesting sensor nodes over random channel gains. It involves wireless communication, energy harvesting, and optimization. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
